function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	--make Maltorius clone, move him into place, say the line, delete him 
	local clone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actorNecroNPCInvisible)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(clone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(clone, actorNecroNPC, "NPC_Walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(clone, actorNecroNPC)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convIntro, idSelf, clone)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(clone)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	local clone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actorNecroNPC)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(clone) then
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(clone, 3.0)
	end
	
end
